Import the fatty acid composition dataset

fattyAcidComposition.Rd

fattyAcidComposition returns a data frame with data about the fatty acid composition of microbes.

fattyAcidComposition()

Value

A tidy data frame of fattyAcidComposition from customlinks.tsv

Examples
